title: Don't Lose Your Cool - Smyths Toys
description:
Inspired by viral challenges that have gathered billions of views across the Internet, this game tests one's ability to remain calm under pressure. Players wear the Cool-O-metre unit that measures heart rate, and the opposing team rolls the dice that will determine how they'll try to get a player to get flustered. For example, opponents might have to get up close to the player and sniff them, or make pig noises. If the player reacts -laughs, cringes, flinches, etc., their heart rate may go up and the metre will rise. They might think that they can hide their reactions, but the Cool-O-metre will show what's really going on! When the metre gets high enough, the lights go to red, the alarm will sound, and the opponent wins that round for making them lose their composure.

Buy online at https://www.smythstoys.com/uk/en-gb/toys/games-puzzles-and-books/board-games/social-games/don-t-lose-your-cool/p/167442

description:

The lightweight frame and wide one piece, non slip plastic deck offerS support and comfort to your child while they are perfecting their coordination skills with the 'lean and steer' technology. The curved handle bar of the Cruz Scooter features non-slip handle bar grips with larger bar end to keep their little hands in place while riding. This is an important feature for younger children as they are stood upright it helps them to be more aware of their surroundings whilst aiding the development of good posture and also making the Zycom Cruz easier to ride.

title: Smyths Toys - Project Mc2 Doll's
description:
Project Mc2 Doll McKeyla's Light Bulb
Now you can perform an experiment at home with Project Mc2 leader, McKeyla McAlister. Make your own glitter globe light again and again using safe household ingredients like water, glitter and glycerine.

Picking Up S.T.E.A.M! Most people know that wires conduct electricity, but did you know that tap water can as well? To turn on the light, you need electricity to flow from the battery to the light and back -- a complete circuit. Turning the bulb right side up allows electricity to flow through the water and reach the light. You add glycerine because it thickens the water, making it more like syrup. Now, the glitter will fall slower.

Project Mc2 is a team of four super-smart and seriously cool girls who use their love of science and their spy skills as they go on missions for secret organization, NOV8 (that's â€˜innovateâ€™!). They're real girls with real skills ready to take on anything. Watch new episodes of the Project Mc2 original series, only on Netflix!
Buy online at http://www.smythstoys.com/ie/en-ie/toys/fashion-dolls/c-513/other-fashion-dolls/p-20039/project-mc2-doll-mckeyla-s-light-bulb/

Project Mc2 Doll Ember's Garden
Now you can perform an experiment at home with earthy scientist and newest member of Project Mc2, Ember Evergreen. Make your own hanging garden using safe household ingredients like soil and plant seeds.

Picking Up S.T.E.A.M! There's science to gardening. Your clear container, called a terrarium, is like an aquarium for plants. Itâ€™s a mini-world in there! The plants inside need less water because the container helps trap moisture. Some of the water in the terrarium is reused through a three-step water cycle - (1) water evaporates, (2) water vapor cools to make droplets when it touches the container, (3) water droplets drip back down to the plant.

Buy online at http://www.smythstoys.com/uk/en-gb/toys/fashion-dolls/c-513/other-fashion-dolls/p-20041/project-mc2-doll-ember-s-garden/

Project Mc2 Doll Bryden's Panda Speaker
Now you can perform an experiment at home with tech genius, Bryden Bandweth. Make your own panda-shaped speaker using safe household ingredients like apple slices.

Picking Up S.T.E.A.M! Smartphones and computers convert your favorite songs into a series of electrical pulses. These electrical pulses are sent to the panda speaker and back in a circular path -- a complete circuit. When you feed an apple slice to the panda, you complete the path and the electricity reaches the speaker. You can now hear the music! If any part of this path is broken, the speaker wonâ€™t work. This means that apples can conduct electricity!

Buy online at http://www.smythstoys.com/uk/en-gb/toys/fashion-dolls/c-513/other-fashion-dolls/p-19663/project-mc2-doll-bryden-s-panda-speaker/

Project Mc2 Doll Devon's Paint
Now you can perform an experiment at home with artist extraordinaire and newest member of Project Mc2, Devon D'Marco. Make your own puffy paint using safe household ingredients like flour, salt, powdered drink mix, and food colouring.

Picking Up S.T.E.A.M! Mix Art with S.T.E.M. to make S.T.E.A.M. Each ingredient in the puffy paint plays a special role. The flour makes the paint thicker so it doesnâ€™t leak out of the tube. The salt forms crystals when the paint dries making it appear sparkly, and the drink mix and food colouring provide the colour. After we apply the paint, a process called evaporation removes the water, leaving a lot of flour and salt behind, making it appear puffy.

Project Mc2 Doll Adrienne's Bath Fizz
You can perform an experiment at home with Adrienne Attoms, Project Mc2's resident culinary chemist (yes, it's a thing!). Make your own bath fizz using safe household ingredients like baking soda, citric acid and vanilla.

Picking Up S.T.E.A.M! Usually, you use the classic reaction of baking soda (a base) and vinegar (an acid) to create carbon dioxide gas bubbles. This time, we use citric acid instead of vinegar because it is a solid. You can now pre-mix it with baking soda, mold it into a ball, and then activate it later by putting the ball in water to create fizzy bubbles. The other ingredients -- such as vanilla, glitter, sprinkles, and food colouring â€“ just make your bath more relaxing and fun.

title: Smyths Toys - Tetris Dual
description:
Tetris Dual is a head to head, table top strategy game, based on Tetris, one of the most popular electronic games of all time. The object is simple, play the Tetrimino shapes displayed on the LCD screen by dropping them into the Matrix (play grid). Score points by placing a piece next to one of your own colour, but score more points by completing a full row. Don't leave any holes or you will lose points. Then press the return button to pass play to your opponent. Use strategy to block your opponent, making it easier to play your remaining Tetriminos and complete the most rows.

Game 1. SPEED - only 60 seconds to complete each turn. Lose points if the timer runs out.

Game 2. COUNTDOWN - with a running countdown, score bonus points if you complete the game with the most time remaining...who will be the first to play all of their Tetriminos and score the most points?
